# Profile Images Storage

This directory is used to store user profile images uploaded through the RideYaari platform.

## Storage Configuration

- **Bucket Name**: profile-images
- **Access**: Public read access for profile images
- **File Types**: JPG, PNG, GIF
- **Max File Size**: 5MB
- **Naming Convention**: {user_id}-{timestamp}.{extension}

## Security

- Users can only upload images to their own profile
- File type validation is enforced
- File size limits are enforced
- Old images are automatically deleted when new ones are uploaded